disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Love Tap.

blurb.value: Miss Fortune deals bonus physical damage whenever she attacks a new target.

description.value: Innate: Miss Fortune's next basic attack against an enemy unit ( turrets included) that was not the target of her previous basic attack, will deal 50% − 100% (based on level) AD bonus physical damage, halved to 25% − 50% (based on level) AD against minions.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * With Runaan's Hurricane, Love Tap only applies to the primary target. The bonus damage applies  life steal.
notes.description: Displays additional information with effect table to the right.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Double Up.

target range.value: Miss Fortune's  attack range

blurb.value: Miss Fortune fires a bullet at an enemy, damaging them and a target behind them. Both strikes can also apply Love Tap.

description.value: Active: Miss Fortune fires a shot at the target enemy that deals physical damage, which then bounces to hit another enemy behind it. The shot applies on-hit effects to both enemies hit, and applies on-attack effects for the first enemy hit.

description2.value: Double Up's bounce prioritizes units directly behind the primary target.

description3.value: Double Up's bounce is affected by critical strike modifiers. If Double Up kills its primary target, the bounce will critically strike.

description4.value: The shot bounces to the enemy regardless of having sight of them or not.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * Spell shields can be used by either target. If it is on the primary target, the spell shield will not prevent the shot from bouncing. The second shot follows a priority order on targets within 500 units of the primary one: Enemy or neutral units within a 20º cone. Enemy or neutral units within a 40º cone. Enemy or neutral units within a 110º cone. Enemy or neutral units within 150 units in a 160º cone. Double Up's cast range adjusts based on Miss Fortune's  attack range, which can be increased by items such as Rapid Firecannon. The damage of a critically striking second shot is 40 / 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 (+ 200% AD) (+ 70% AP) physical damage. If there is no secondary target, the shot will not bounce and the dud will instead fall to the ground. The dud lands on the ground 176 units behind the primary target and has a missile speed of 400 on its journey there.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Strut.

blurb.value: Miss Fortune passively gains Movement Speed when not attacked. This ability can be activated to grant bonus Attack Speed for a short duration. While it's on cooldown, Love Taps reduce the remaining cooldown of Strut.

description.value: Passive: Miss Fortune gains  25 bonus movement speed if she has not taken non- persistent damage in the last 5 seconds. This bonus is increased to a greater amount after another 5 seconds.

description2.value: Active: Miss Fortune gains  bonus attack speed for 4 seconds and brings Strut's passive effect to full power.

description3.value: Marking a new target with Love Tap reduces Strut's  cooldown by 2 seconds.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Bullet Time.

blurb.value: Miss Fortune channels a flurry of bullets into a cone in front of her, dealing large amounts of damage to enemies. Each wave of Bullet Time can critically strike.

description.value: Active: Miss Fortune channels for 3 seconds while firing several waves of bullets in a spread of 6 projectiles per wave in the target direction, with each wave dealing 75% AD (+ 20% AP) physical damage to enemies hit.

description2.value: Each wave can critically strike, dealing (20% +  5%) bonus physical damage.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * The damage dealt by each wave of Bullet Time is calculated when the wave reaches the target. Targets cannot be damaged by more than one projectile per wave. The bullet streams that each fire 1 projectile per wave are spead by 6° between one another, aiming towards the angles +-3/9/15° from Miss Fortune's facing direction. Bullet time picks 6 locations on the ground 500 units from Miss Fortune (with the aforementioned angles) at the start of the channel and fires a bullet stream towards each. If Miss Fortune is teleported to a new location, these locations will not update; the cone will fire towards Miss Fortune's original position, thinning down or spreading out based on distance from the group of locations. Bullet time fires the first wave at 0.066 seconds, and the last at 2.904 seconds. Times between waves are equally spread between these values. Miss Fortune may cancel the last ~0.1 seconds of channel time at no loss of effect. Waves that critically strike deal 90% AD physical damage (+ 24% AP), increased to 93.75 AD (+ 25% AP) with Infinity Edge. If every single wave was a critical strike, the total damage would be 1080 / 1170 / 1260 / 1350 / 1440% AD (+ 288 / 312 / 336 / 360 / 384% AP), increased to 1125 / 1218.75 / 1312.5 / 1406.25 / 1500% AD (+ 300 / 325 / 350 / 375 / 400% AP) with Infinity Edge.
